--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a68dcd5d31e684d4f8fa33d4ccd3de02, type: 3}
  m_Name: Leopar
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::SoulData
  soulName: Prens Rawfield
  baseSprite: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
  fullBackstory: "Lakap: Kay\u0131p Hanedan\u0131n Son Varisi / Beneklilerin H\xFCk\xFCmdar\u0131\n\r\nGe\xE7mi\u015F:
    \xD6nceki hayat\u0131nda leoparlar \xFCzerinde h\xFCk\xFCm s\xFCren bir prensti
    ve taht\u0131n son varisiydi.\n\r\n\xD6l\xFCm \u015Fekli: Hayvan krall\u0131\u011F\u0131nda
    bir sava\u015Fta \xF6ld\xFC.\n\r\nSon s\xF6z\xFC: \"ROOOAARRRR, SEN\u0130 HA\u0130N
    P\u0130\xC7!\""
  soulCoins: 12
  dialogueLines:
  - text: Sen... bir memur musun?
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
  - text: "burnunu \xE7eker) Anl\u0131yorum, bizim gibi bir fani de\u011Filsin yani."
    emotion: 3
    expression: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
  - text: "Daha \xF6nce hi\xE7 kadim yarg\u0131\xE7 g\xF6rmemi\u015Ftim\u2026"
    emotion: 3
    expression: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
  - text: "Hmm, bu arada bu diyarda koku duyumu bozan bir g\xFC\xE7 var."
    emotion: 4
    expression: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
  - text: "Az \xF6nce seni koklad\u0131\u011F\u0131mda daha farkl\u0131 kokuyordun..."
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
  - text: "Yoksa bu, siz \xF6l\xFCms\xFCzlere \xF6zel bir yetenek mi?"
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
  - text: " Neyse, buraya bir kez daha do\u011Fmaya geldim."
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
  - text: "K\xFCllerimden... yeniden do\u011Fmaya."
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
  - text: "Bana yolu g\xF6ster, Yarg\u0131\xE7."
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
  optionA:
    lifeLabel: 12
    lifeDescription: "Onu bir Battle Beast olarak yeniden canland\u0131r "
    coinCost: 12
    bonusSoul: {fileID: 0}
    appearanceDayOffset: 0
    endingSprite: {fileID: -8263878613814959606, guid: 757161d6a9d291d4eaf07437383e3c93, type: 3}
    endingText: "Bulundu\u011Fu evrende ona denk bir varl\u0131k kalmayana kadar
      katleder en sonunda b\xFCt\xFCn bir evrende tek kal\u0131r ve kendi hayat\u0131na
      son verir\u2026"
  optionB:
    lifeLabel: 12
    lifeDescription: "Onu s\u0131radan insan d\xFCnyas\u0131nda Avrupa vatanda\u015F\u0131
      olarak yeniden canland\u0131r"
    coinCost: 12
    bonusSoul: {fileID: 0}
    appearanceDayOffset: 0
    endingSprite: {fileID: 7725894956269620233, guid: b04cc4c54db87bc46b2e23a642037a0f, type: 3}
    endingText: "\u0130talya'da erkek \xE7ocu\u011Fu olarak yeniden do\u011Far ve
      k\xFC\xE7\xFCk ya\u015Fta siyasete ilgi g\xF6sterir. \xDCniversitede avukatl\u0131k
      okur ve mezun olunca ilk i\u015F siyasete girer. Bilerek muhalefette kal\u0131r
      ve asla cumhurba\u015Fkan\u0131 olmaya \xE7al\u0131\u015Fmaz; muhalefette kal\u0131p
      mevcut iktidar\u0131 dara sokman\u0131n ona cumhurba\u015Fkan\u0131 olmaktan
      daha \xE7ok zevk verece\u011Fine inan\u0131r. Ama merak\u0131na yenik d\xFC\u015Fer
      ve se\xE7imlerde \xF6ne \xE7\u0131karak iktidara gelir. \xDClkeyi 60 ya\u015F\u0131na
      kadar y\xF6netir ve iyi durumda tutar; lakin bu i\u015F ve a\u011F\u0131rl\u0131\u011F\u0131
      onu ya\u015Fl\u0131 bir buna\u011Fa \xE7evirmi\u015F, huysuz emekli dedenin
      teki yapm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r. \xC7evresinde kimse kalmaz ve 84 ya\u015F\u0131nda
      tek ba\u015F\u0131na hayata g\xF6zlerini yumar."
